# ENVIRONMENT SETUP FOR ALL SHELLS
# Set $PATH early in case other stuff here needs it.
#
# Skipped under SHRC_LOAD_FUNCTIONS_ONLY (set by the test harness so
# `. ./shrc` populates every shrc function in one shot instead of
# sed-extracting each one via extract_func -- which previously cost
